OL,5, The maximum amount of compensation     
OL,6, households and firms can claim for     
OL,7, power cuts due to storms has nearly    
OL,8, tripled under new rules.               
OL,10,FThe cap has gone up from #700 to       
OL,11,F#2,000, said energy watchdog Ofgem.    
OL,13,FIt follows a review into the response  
OL,14,Fto Storm Arwen, when nearly one million
OL,15,Fhomes and businesses lost power -      
OL,16,Fthousands for several days.            
OL,18,FAn Ofgem director said the "tough new  
OL,19,Frules" would ensure energy companies   
OL,20,Fprepare better for severe weather.     
